ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to (1) align, for clarity, consistency and accuracy, existing provisions of the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations with amendments to the Immigration and Refugee Protection Act; and (2) ensure the expeditious and differentiated processing and removal of certain classes of failed asylum claimants.
